Ё   - Must be x264 (8-bit depth).                                             Ё
Ё   - Must use Matroska (.mkv) for container                                  Ё
Ё   - You will have 30 days from latest  x264  rev date to update in order to Ё
Ё     maintain all bug fixes and improvements in the x264 codec               Ё
Ё   - Stripping or falsifying encode information in the file header is banned Ё
Ё   - Custom  muxing  tools are permitted; however, output must be compatible Ё
Ё     with  standard  demuxers  to  the  same  extent that files created with Ё
Ё     MKVToolnix  are.                                                        Ё
Ё   - Custom Matrices are allowed                                             Ё
