Ё   - Deblocking  must  be  used;  values are at the discretion of the group. Ё
Ё     (default is enabled, 0:0 settings)                                      Ё
Ё   - Sample Aspect Ratio (--sar) must be square (1:1).                       Ё
Ё   - No setting can go below what is specified by --preset slow.             Ё
