Ё  Resolution:                                                                Ё
Ё   - Crop  to  closest  mod2 without under-cropping. Then, if width>1280 or  Ё
Ё     height>720,  resize  so  that the frame fits within 1280x720 and either Ё
Ё     width=1280 or height=720. Never upscale, never add borders.             Ё
Ё   - Crop out everything that was not in the original picture and caused by  Ё
Ё     the  broadcaster.  This includes but is not limited to: black borders,  Ё
Ё     and duplicate lines.  Removing or retaining fading edges is at capper's Ё
Ё     discretion and shall not be considered undercropped or overcropped.     Ё
Ё   - Cropping  should  be  done  to  the  most  common  frame  size  (e.g.   Ё
Ё     pitch/primary view in sports).                                          Ё
Ё   - Actual picture area may be over- or under-cropped by 1px maximum.       Ё
