Ё  Subs:                                                                      Ё
Ё   - Optional, but encouraged                                                Ё
Ё   - Text  based  format  is preferred (e.g. SubRip, SubStation Alpha, etc). Ё
Ё   - Subtitles must be muxed into the MKV. "Subs" directories are forbidden. Ё
Ё   - Burned  subtitles  will  only  be  allowed  when  the  source  exhibits Ё
Ё     such subtitles in the picture itself                                    Ё
Ё   - Multi-language  subtitles  cannot  be  used  as  a  basis  for  a  dupe Ё
Ё   - Group watermarks in subtitles are strictly forbidden.                   Ё
Ё                                                                             Ё
Ё  Packaging:                                                                 Ё
Ё   - Releases must be packed in RAR file format.                             Ё
Ё   - Rars must be in multiples of 50 MB, no more than 99 files               Ё
Ё     1MB = 1,000,000 bytes                                                   Ё
Ё   - Multi-episode  releases  with no clear delineation such as credits must Ё
Ё     not be split                                                            Ё
Ё   - RAR Compression must not be used                                        Ё
Ё   - Recovery and MD5 record are optional                                    Ё
Ё   - Encryption or password protection is forbidden                          Ё
Ё   - Must have SFV and NFO                                                   Ё
Ё   - RAR, SFV, and sample files must have unique, lowercase filenames with   Ё
Ё     the group tag.                                                          Ё
Ё                                                                             Ё
Ё  Credits/Previously On:                                                     Ё
Ё   - It  is  suggested  that  any  previously  on footage be included in the Ё
Ё     release, but it is not required.                                        Ё
Ё   - Full  end  credits  must  be  included  if they contain show content or Ё
Ё     outtakes/bloopers.  End  credits  are  optional  if  they  are clean or Ё
Ё     contain    promotions    for    future   episodes   or   other   shows. Ё
Ё                                                                             Ё
Ё  Samples:                                                                   Ё
Ё   - REQUIRED!                                                               Ё
Ё   - 50-70 seconds in length and  in  a  separate  folder  marked  as Sample Ё
Ё   - Must   be  taken  from  the  episode, i.e.-   not   encoded  separately Ё
Ё   - Stream  samples  are  recommended  for  any questionable issue with the Ё
Ё     source, e.g. no IVTC possible, IVTC to 24.975fps, etc.                  Ё
Ё                                                                             Ё
Ё                                                                             Ё
Ё  Propers:                                                                   Ё
Ё   - Propers  are  only  permitted  in  the  case of a technical flaw in the Ё
Ё     original release (e.g. Bad IVTC, Interlacing, missing footage, resizing Ё
Ё     720p source, bad crop, commercials, bad x264 settings used, bad source, Ё
Ё     etc.)                                                                   Ё
Ё   - Scrolling messages added by a station (e.g. weather, Amber alerts) must Ё
Ё     be   at   least   30   seconds   in  length  in  order  to  nuke/proper Ё
Ё   - After exceptions, over- or under-cropping by > 1px is considered a      Ё
Ё     technical flaw.                                                         Ё
Ё   - Proper  reason  must  be clearly stated in nfo, including timecodes and Ё
Ё     extent of the flaw when appropriate                                     Ё
Ё   - Sample of propered release is encouraged                                Ё
Ё   - Qualitative propers are not allowed                                     Ё
Ё   - Flaws  (such  as  drops) present in any optional content are not a flaw Ё
Ё     and shall not be nuked or propered.                                     Ё
Ё   - Propers  based  upon  the  rules  set  forth  here  are allowed only on Ё
Ё     releases that come after this document is made public                   Ё
Ё                                                                             Ё
Ё  Internals:                                                                 Ё
Ё   - Internals  are  allowed  to  be pred for any reason, including releases Ё
Ё     with technical flaws or those done with alternate codecs, containers,   Ё
Ё     or settings for experimental purposes.                                  Ё
Ё   - Any severe technical flaws or deviations must be mentioned in the NFO.  Ё
Ё   - With the exception of the following rule, internal releases may only be Ё
Ё     nuked for severe technical flaws or deviations that are not mentioned   Ё
Ё     in the NFO.                                                             Ё
Ё   - Using  INTERNAL.DIRFIX  as  a  cheap  attempt  at  avoiding  a  nuke is Ё
Ё     forbidden.  If  the  release  is technically flawed, it is still deemed Ё
Ё     nukable  both  before  and  after  an attempted INTERNAL.DIRFIX and the Ё
Ё     DIRFIX shall be nuked for fix.for.nuke.                                 Ё
