Ё  Nukes:                                                                     Ё
Ё   Releases must be nuked for any of the following reasons:                  Ё
Ё   - Any valid proper listed in the propers section                          Ё
Ё   - Missing nfo, or missing Sample                                          Ё
Ё   - Invalid directory naming format                                         Ё
Ё   - Mislabeled  directory  that  could  prevent  finding  the  release in a Ё
Ё     dupecheck,  including  incorrect season/episode/date or incorrect title Ё
Ё   - Dupe                                                                    Ё
